{"tid":939304,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鬥曬命 月入6位數李生: 3萬一呎都買 溫小姐1,400萬買自住","createTime":"2018-12-13T04:14:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-13T10:49:35.000Z","uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"8b414cd10c396e3cca587ce55f61a02c2cbe3b15","tid":939304,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T04:14:10.000Z","msg":"買家李生表示，居住於觀塘區已經28年，見證觀塘裕民坊重建，等了10年終於推盤，故立即購買。是次斥資1,000萬元購入凱滙2房單位，首期預一半，打算用作收租投資，直言該盤開價即使「3萬都會買」，因為住在觀塘28年有感情。他透露自己從事物流業，月入約6位數。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181213/large/1544672733_cbc2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181213%2Flarge%2F1544672733_cbc2.jpg&h=2165470d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n李生指住在觀塘28年有感情，於是即刻買凱滙(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n居住紅磡的買家溫小姐斥資1,400萬購入凱滙中層3房單位，首期預算一半，直言價格好有誠意，加上自己曾於該區返工覺得好方便，而入票後抽中，覺得有緣分就買。是次購入將會用以自住。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181213/large/1544673792_128b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181213%2Flarge%2F1544673792_128b.jpg&h=bc4b1b42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />6位數收入，有冇交足稅？"},{"pid":"da64710536016ac3610443a22d57ecaf40a03fbb","tid":939304,"uid":18966,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T04:16:00.000Z","msg":"李生果樣咁支那"},{"pid":"0b1fc340dec80edd4b4725ece6030c13278f30c2","tid":939304,"uid":184010,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T04:16:01.000Z","msg":"香港有錢人多撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d62970c186b09c4f4fef99a0ca83fee99b55fe76","tid":939304,"uid":29041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T04:18:13.000Z","msg":"買個三萬蚊個盤比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ece8900eccdb468c34ed1d8f7